hcc_text: Sixth Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Brooklyn)
info: At Sixth Avenue at Gowanus Exwy Wb Exit 21, Erik Place and 65th Street, there were 3 severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
